[I] Bookmark organizer and editor

[T] The editor shows a tree view of your KDE bookmarks and bookmark subfolders.
[T] Several applications in the KDE suite let you create bookmarks (e.g.
[T] Konqueror, Konsole, Konversation) and will launch this bookmark editor from
[T] their Bookmarks -> Edit Bookmarks menu item.

[U] https://www.kde.org

[A] The KDE-Team
[M] Rene Rebe <rene@t2-project.org>

